Just to increase the paranoia people may want to read
  
http://www.cs.auckland.ac.nz/~pgut001/pubs/secure_del.html
In particular the stuff about recovery of data from DRAMs and SRAMS is
interesting even though probably only people believe orange book class A
certied systems are as insecure as DOS should really worry about that.
But since Wasenaar we know that they're out to get us ;-)
